<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
/agree<P>A shaman can melee.  A shaman cannot melee as well as a melee class.  We have many other options at our disposal for doing damage, and in most circumstances are better served by using them.<P>This is not an endorsement of the shaman as a weakling who should sit down, shut up, and stay out of the way.  By all means, get up and poke that mob.  If your tanks get uppity, solo a mob right in front of them, and show them what you can do.  I have kept my offense/defense/piercing maxed, and reccomend the same for all shaman.  Just realize that you may not be best served by swinging a weapon.<P>SLurm!<P>--------------------<P>Slurm Fearbringer<BR>51st Iksar Shaman -E'ci<BR>Pillars of Heaven -officer
</FONT>
