As Blarg observed, shaman taunt better with their spells than with their weapons.  If a cleric lays down a heal or a caster overnukes or gets a mez resisted on the adds, you will probably not do enough damage in your first one or two attacks to peel off the mob.  But a slow or dot will do it right away.
